Andy Dufresne - if he has been dead for 20 seconds and the heat he died in is still going he will be spun back in again.
shelob - After 3 seconds of not being hit it starts crawling around random directions on its 8 legs. It won't walk off of its ow accord.
The prestige - There are two version of this entity that enter twice in the tournament. They can be in the same heat or other heats to start.
The obelisk - spawns an obelisk bumper at a random point on the map that acts like the bumpers in the final round
kill bill - do 5x damage vs an enery who is randomly selected at the start of the heat (it will pick again if it plays a second round)
american psycho - damage resets after 20 seconds
Little miss sunshine - Doesn't take damage from any beyblades that are remotely blue or red
